snippet.title: Alan Wake 2: The Lake House - Launch Trailer | Xbox Partner Preview October 2024
snippet.description:
The Lake House is a mysterious facility set up on the shores of Cauldron Lake by the Federal Bureau of Control to conduct secret research... until something goes wrong. Explore the twisted sub-levels of the Lake House as you descend into a harrowing survival horror experience, where the realities of the Pacific Northwest and the Dark Place collide once again.

As Agent Estevez, you’ll explore the twisted halls of the multi-storied Lake House, and unravel the dark secrets hidden within.

Developed by Remedy Entertainment & Published by Epic Games Inc.
